Rules.InvariantScript:
"Welcome, "& Parent.compUser &"!
Today is: " & Concatenate(Text( Today(), "dddd" ),", ",Text( Today(), "dd/mm/yy" )) & ""

SortByColumns(
    Distinct(
        Filter(
        colReportedData,
        If(!IsEmpty(cmbSystem.SelectedItems),SystemERP in cmbSystem.SelectedItems,true),
        If(!IsEmpty(cmbEntityName.SelectedItems),BusinessUnit in cmbEntityName.SelectedItems,true)
        ),
        Currency
    ),
    "Result"
)

SortByColumns(
    Distinct(
        Filter(
        colReportedData,
        If(!IsEmpty(cmbSystem.SelectedItems),SystemERP in cmbSystem.SelectedItems,true),
        If(!IsEmpty(cmbEntityName.SelectedItems),BusinessUnit in cmbEntityName.SelectedItems,true),
        If(!IsEmpty(cmbAccCurr.SelectedItems),Currency in cmbAccCurr.SelectedItems,true)
        ),
        Account
    ),
    "Result"
)

SortByColumns(
    Distinct(
        Filter(
            colReportedData,
            If(!IsEmpty(cmbSystem.SelectedItems),SystemERP in cmbSystem.SelectedItems,true),
            If(!IsEmpty(cmbEntityName.SelectedItems),BusinessUnit in cmbEntityName.SelectedItems,true),
            If(!IsEmpty(cmbAccCurr.SelectedItems),Currency in cmbAccCurr.SelectedItems,true),
            If(!IsEmpty(cmbAccNo.SelectedItems),Account in cmbAccNo.SelectedItems,true)
        ),
        Text(StatementDate, "dd/mm/yy")
    ),
    "Result"
)

SortByColumns(
    Filter(
        colReportedData,
        If(
            !IsBlank(cmbSystem.Selected.Result),
            SystemERP in cmbSystem.SelectedItems,
            true
        ),
        If(
            !IsBlank(cmbEntityName.Selected.Result),
            BusinessUnit in cmbEntityName.SelectedItems,
            true
        ),
        If(
            !IsBlank(cmbAccCurr.Selected.Result),
            Currency in cmbAccCurr.SelectedItems,
            true
        ),
        If(
            !IsBlank(cmbAccNo.Selected.Result),
            Account in cmbAccNo.SelectedItems,
            true
        ),
        If(
            !IsBlank(cmbStatDate.Selected.Result),
            Text(StatementDate,"dd/mm/yy") in cmbStatDate.SelectedItems,
            true
        ),
        If(
            !IsBlank(cmbUserName.Selected.Result),
            User.DisplayName in cmbUserName.Selected.Result,
            true
        )
    ),
    varSortBy,
    If(
        varSortOrder,
        Ascending,
        Descending
    )
)
